children.text: In March 2025, the legendary Lakarschneid face at Kitzsteinhorn once again became the epicenter of the international freeride scene. As a vital part of the newly expanded FWT Challenger series, the X OVER RIDE attracts a diverse field of ambitious riders from around the globe, all united by one goal: securing a spot for the 2026 Freeride World Tour.

The atmosphere in Zell am See-Kaprun is defined by a unique blend of high-stakes competition and deep-rooted community spirit. While the 'Public Viewing Area' at Langwied buzzes with fans and experts, the riders face a grueling challenge on the mountain. With only a few coveted tickets available for the world's elite class, every line choice and every drop counts. These photographs capture the essence of this showdown—showcasing the raw energy of the runs and the dedication of an international community that lives for the mountains. It is more than a contest; it is the decisive battleground for the next generation of freeride talent.

seoDescription: Action gallery from X OVER RIDE 2025 at Kitzsteinhorn. Witness the FWT Challenger highlights as elite riders battle for a spot on the Freeride World Tour.
title: X OVER RIDE - FWT Challenger

ODYSSEY is more than just a mountain bike edit; it’s a journey back to the roots of the sport. Filmed at the rugged Hochwechsel on the border of Lower Austria and Styria, this project captures the soul of the infamous Wexl Trails.
Inspired by the raw energy of early 2000s adventure films, ODYSSEY steps away from high-gloss perfection. It’s about the grit and the honesty of the ride. No over-the-top effects—just pure mountain biking in its most authentic form.

The film follows the team starting at 4:00 AM in freezing conditions at 1,743 meters. Between sea-of-fog vistas and frozen fingers, the production reflects the dedication that drives this community. It’s a visual story of passion, nature, and the timeless spirit of adventure on two wheels.
Rider: Manuel Mayer
Camera+Cut: Fabian Trummer
Camera+VFX: Matthias Michelic
Music: Savanah
Support: Wexl Trails, Banana Crew, Savanah, LINES & Friesi’s Bikery

seoDescription: Experience ODYSSEY, a raw mountain bike journey at Hochwechsel. Inspired by early 2000s freeride films, focusing on pure passion, the Wexl Trails community, and the beauty of the Austrian Alps.
title: Odyssea – An MTB Adventure

children.text: The Gnarathon is more than just a contest; it’s a three-day riot of creativity, inclusivity, and raw adrenaline. From the soulful FLINTA* sessions at Währinger Park to the high-octane madness at the Ottakringer Brewery, the 2025 edition proved why this event is a cornerstone of the European scene. It wasn’t just about the tricks—though the skating was nothing short of "mental"—it was about the bridge between art, music, and the streets.

Capturing this event meant diving headfirst into the mosh pits and dodging flying boards to document the heartbeat of the community. Whether it was the quiet moments of a rooftop art show or the deafening roar of punk rock during a heavy session, the spirit of the Gnarathon remained the same: everyone is welcome, provided you bring the energy. This series is a tribute to the skaters, the fans, and the legends who keep the DIY spirit of Vienna alive.

seoDescription: Experience the energy of Gnarathon Vienna 2025. A three-day celebration of skateboarding culture, featuring FLINTA* sessions, Ottakringer Beer and pure community spirit.
title: Gnarathon Vienna 2025
